data.description: Discover your dream home! This property offers an array of desirable features for a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Enjoy worry-free living with the HOA covering exterior maintenance, including the roof, providing peace of mind. Embrace accessibility with no stairs, perfect for all ages. The covered patio invites outdoor enjoyment in any weather. Stay organized with an extra storage closet. Revel in contemporary elegance with new vinyl plank flooring, complementing any interior design. Benefit from two full baths for added convenience and privacy. Cozy up next to the gas log fireplace on chilly evenings. Beat the summer heat with central air conditioning. The kitchen pantry offers ample storage space. Stay comfortable with lighted ceiling fans thoughtfully placed throughout. Display your favorite items on built-in shelves. The walk-in closet provides efficient storage for your wardrobe. Indulge in the private oasis of the primary ensuite bath. A washer/dryer is included for added convenience. With a deeded parking space, parking is stress-free. This exceptional property offers hassle-free maintenance and thoughtful amenities, enhancing everyday living. Don't miss out on this opportunity for a life of comfort and luxury. Schedule a viewing today and step into the future of homeownership! *****Brand new carpet was just installed.*****
